data.description: Want to feel like your living in the Mountains, but are just seconds away from town? This property could be for you! Proudly offering over 2800 sqft, this affordable home in Wetumpka is ready for your Family! Park in the two car garage, and be welcomed by this all brick home! This home has one thing, SPACE! Space for everything! Through the front door, there is a HUGE formal living area, that makes a great bonus room! Continue through the dining room and past the oversized laundry room, a large kitchen with TONS of cabinets await! Start your family meals while watching deer come right to your back door, or get a better look from the screened in porch! The living room is large - perfect for family movie night! Continue down the hall, and the master bedroom await - large in size and  easily hold king size furniture, complete with master ensuite. The other three bedrooms are tucked away and all have large closets and share a full bathroom. If you have too many things, no problem! This home has PLENTY of storage! From the multitude of closets, all the way down to the oversize garage, you have plenty of options for all of your storage needs! Outback is a patio that runs almost the entire length of the home! Great for family gatherings and outdoor hangouts! This property is ready for a new family to enjoy! Call today!
